HELM:

Helm is a package 
helm 3

yum
npm
apt
brew
choco

curl -fsSL -o get_helm.sh https://raw.githubusercontent.com/helm/helm/master/scripts/get-helm-3
chmod 700 get_helm.sh
./get_helm.sh


we can use helm to install third party application and also custom application.
like: nginx , prometheus and grafana, datadog, efk
springapp

helm create springapp

springapp/
├── Chart.yaml
├── charts
├── templates
│   ├── NOTES.txt
│   ├── _helpers.tpl
│   ├── deployment.yaml
│   ├── hpa.yaml
│   ├── ingress.yaml
│   ├── service.yaml
│   ├── serviceaccount.yaml
│   └── tests
│       └── test-connection.yaml
└── values.yaml


##HELMS INSTALLATION## 
wget https://get.helm.sh/helm-v3.4.1-linux-amd64.tar.gz 
tar xvf helm-v3.4.1-linux-amd64.tar.gz 
sudo mv linux-amd64/helm /usr/local/bin 
rm helm-v3.4.1-linux-amd64.tar.gz 
rm -rf linux-amd64 
helm version 
